#CHIP K053260
#CLOCK 8000000

; K053260 (Konami PCM) Basic Test
;
; The K053260 is a Konami custom PCM chip used in various arcade games.
; It has 4 channels of 16-bit PCM playback.
;
; Tests:
; - All 4 channels with basic sample playback
; - Volume control
; - Pan positioning

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; Channel 1: Sample 1
c4 .

; Channel 2: Sample 2
d4 .

; Channel 3: Sample 3
e4 .

; Channel 4: Sample 4
f4 .

r4

; All 4 channels together
c4 & d4 & e4 & f4 .

r4

; Staccato pattern
c4 . d4 . e4 . f4 .

r2

#END
